01:12:20,379 --> 01:12:22,250
PHILIP: Come to Daddy.
XAVIER: We're so worried.

1016
01:12:22,294 --> 01:12:24,122
I wanna go home now.
Are you okay?

1017
01:12:25,384 --> 01:12:26,820
The car's in the car park.

1018
01:12:26,864 --> 01:12:28,474
PHILIP: Come on, little one.
Let's get you home.

1019
01:12:28,518 --> 01:12:30,346
SOPHIE: It's very funny here.

1020
01:12:38,963 --> 01:12:41,052
Thank God you're here.

1021
01:12:45,056 --> 01:12:46,362
She's going to be okay.

1022
01:13:25,096 --> 01:13:26,750
[LIGHTNING CRACKING]

1023
01:13:46,509 --> 01:13:48,380
How long have we
known each other?

1024
01:13:50,164 --> 01:13:52,384
Almost three weeks.

1025
01:14:00,131 --> 01:14:02,307
I feel like I've lived
a lifetime with you.

1026
01:14:25,548 --> 01:14:27,158
[THUNDER RUMBLING]

1027
01:14:30,683 --> 01:14:32,990
The weather changes so quickly.

1028
01:15:00,757 --> 01:15:02,541
[MAN CHATTERING ON TV]

1029
01:15:03,890 --> 01:15:05,501
[PHONE RINGING]

1030
01:15:09,287 --> 01:15:10,636
Hello? MO: Hi, it's me.

1031
01:15:10,680 --> 01:15:13,683
Mo! What time is it there?
Are you okay?

1032
01:15:13,726 --> 01:15:16,381
Oh, I just wanted
to hear your voice.

1033
01:15:18,557 --> 01:15:21,429
I guess I'm getting
kind of homesick.

1034
01:15:21,952 --> 01:15:23,693
Oh, Mo. Why don't you come home?

1035
01:15:23,736 --> 01:15:26,826
We're all here waiting
for you and we miss you.

1036
01:15:26,870 --> 01:15:29,525
Oh, and the damn rabbit got
lost. Jenny was so upset.

1037
01:15:29,568 --> 01:15:30,613
She's sleeping right
here, beside me.

1038
01:15:30,656 --> 01:15:32,266
Do you want to speak
to her? Jenny.

1039
01:15:32,310 --> 01:15:34,878
Oh, no, no, no. Don't wake her.

1040
01:15:36,575 --> 01:15:37,881
Oh, okay.

1041
01:15:38,621 --> 01:15:41,754
Hi, Jenny. No. Don't you  
worry about Harvey.

1042
01:15:41,798 --> 01:15:43,364
He'll be fine.

1043
01:15:43,408 --> 01:15:46,106
That's what Mommy said, but
who's gonna take care of him?

1044
01:15:46,150 --> 01:15:48,544
Take care?

1045
01:15:48,587 --> 01:15:51,547
You know wabbits.
They're a lot like people.

1046
01:15:51,590 --> 01:15:53,853
It's hard for them to be alone.

1047
01:15:53,897 --> 01:15:56,116
He probably went
looking for a wife.

1048
01:16:07,954 --> 01:16:09,739
[CHATTERING IN FRENCH]

1049
01:16:14,657 --> 01:16:16,789
[MAID CHATTERING IN ITALIAN]

1050
01:16:26,451 --> 01:16:28,409
[THANKING IN ITALIAN]

1051
01:16:28,453 --> 01:16:30,411
Xavier?

1052
01:16:30,455 --> 01:16:32,022
[CHATTERING IN FRENCH]

1053
01:17:05,229 --> 01:17:06,404
[DOOR CLOSING]

1054
01:17:12,845 --> 01:17:14,673
I'm looking for my keys.

1055
01:17:17,589 --> 01:17:19,547
Jenny's rabbit ran away.

1056
01:17:19,591 --> 01:17:20,853
She was real upset.

1057
01:17:20,897 --> 01:17:22,072
Oh. Too bad.

1058
01:17:23,421 --> 01:17:24,727
[KEYS JANGLING]

1059
01:17:28,426 --> 01:17:30,167
Can I talk to you for a second?

1060
01:17:30,210 --> 01:17:31,690
Not now, I'm late.

1061
01:17:31,734 --> 01:17:33,997
I have to make
my reservation today.

1062
01:17:34,040 --> 01:17:35,433
Okay, do it.

1063
01:17:36,695 --> 01:17:38,305
We'll have to decide on a date.

1064
01:17:38,349 --> 01:17:40,568
If I went there last minute,
the flights will be full.

1065
01:17:40,612 --> 01:17:41,439
It's up to you.

1066
01:17:47,401 --> 01:17:49,273
[LAURENCE SPEAKS FRENCH]

1067
01:17:50,840 --> 01:17:52,711
[BIRDS SQUAWKING]

1068
01:18:02,895 --> 01:18:04,854
[CONVERSING IN FRENCH]

1069
01:18:09,206 --> 01:18:10,207
"Tomorrow"...

1070
01:18:10,250 --> 01:18:11,556
[SPEAKING FRENCH]

1071
01:18:11,599 --> 01:18:14,820
We go in avion a America.

1072
01:18:14,864 --> 01:18:16,213
[SPEAKING FRENCH]

1073
01:18:21,566 --> 01:18:22,567
[CHUCKLES]

1074
01:18:41,978 --> 01:18:43,588
[THANKING IN FRENCH]

1075
01:18:45,416 --> 01:18:46,460
Hello.

