1108
01:21:04,033 --> 01:21:07,036
The man who designed it never  lived to see its completion.

1109
01:22:16,801 --> 01:22:18,455
[INDISTINCT CHATTERING]

1110
01:22:34,340 --> 01:22:35,776
[SCREAMING]

1111
01:22:35,820 --> 01:22:36,995
WOMAN: Stop him! Hey!

1112
01:22:39,563 --> 01:22:41,173
[GRUNTING]

1113
01:22:43,045 --> 01:22:44,350
[SCREAMING]

1114
01:22:48,354 --> 01:22:49,965
[SIREN WAILING]

1115
01:23:01,019 --> 01:23:02,847
[CONVERSING IN FRENCH]

1116
01:23:16,861 --> 01:23:18,515
[SPEAKS FRENCH]

1117
01:23:20,952 --> 01:23:23,520
[CHUCKLES] What happened to you?

1118
01:23:24,956 --> 01:23:26,479
I fell in the river.

1119
01:23:26,523 --> 01:23:28,786
[CHUCKLES] How did you do that?

1120
01:23:30,875 --> 01:23:32,790
I went on the Bateaux-Mouches.

1121
01:23:33,747 --> 01:23:36,750
Mo, I warned you about that.

1122
01:23:36,794 --> 01:23:39,536
Xavier, you really piss me off.

1123
01:23:39,579 --> 01:23:42,234
I'm going to bed.
Goodbye and good night.

1124
01:23:44,976 --> 01:23:47,196
Why do you always run away?

1125
01:23:47,239 --> 01:23:48,414
Why do you always lie?

1126
01:23:48,458 --> 01:23:50,677
Every time you get upset,
you run away.

1127
01:23:50,721 --> 01:23:52,636
Answer me, damn it!

1128
01:23:53,202 --> 01:23:54,768
Answer what?

1129
01:23:54,812 --> 01:23:56,205
Where were you?

1130
01:23:56,248 --> 01:23:57,380
You know where I was.

1131
01:23:57,423 --> 01:23:59,164
Say it!

1132
01:23:59,208 --> 01:24:00,644
I was with Nathalie.

1133
01:24:03,212 --> 01:24:05,214
Doesn't matter anyway.

1134
01:24:05,257 --> 01:24:07,607
This time tomorrow,
I'll be in New York.

1135
01:24:11,394 --> 01:24:12,395
I was afraid.

1136
01:24:17,574 --> 01:24:18,618
Did you

1137
01:24:20,794 --> 01:24:22,622
make love to her?

1138
01:24:23,928 --> 01:24:25,103
I couldn't.

1139
01:24:39,161 --> 01:24:41,424
You know, my life,

1140
01:24:42,120 --> 01:24:43,339
it was

1141
01:24:44,427 --> 01:24:47,256
a fine, good structure.

1142
01:24:49,432 --> 01:24:52,435
And I worked hard
to keep it that way.

1143
01:24:54,132 --> 01:24:55,264
And now,

1144
01:24:56,830 --> 01:24:58,789
it's falling apart.

1145
01:25:04,142 --> 01:25:04,969
Don't go away.

1146
01:25:05,839 --> 01:25:06,971
Please.

1147
01:25:13,499 --> 01:25:15,719
Maybe I'm not very clear.

1148
01:25:17,199 --> 01:25:19,114
I'm trying to tell you

1149
01:25:19,157 --> 01:25:20,289
I'm love with you.

1150
01:25:25,163 --> 01:25:25,990
[MOUTHING]

1151
01:25:29,341 --> 01:25:30,560
[LAUGHING]

1152
01:25:35,869 --> 01:25:36,696
Ah!

1153
01:25:43,834 --> 01:25:45,531
I love you. I love you.

1154
01:25:49,187 --> 01:25:50,014
Ah!

1155
01:25:53,191 --> 01:25:54,714
I'm starving. 
Are you?

1156
01:25:56,499 --> 01:25:58,153
Okay, I'll cook today.

1157
01:25:58,196 --> 01:26:00,067
You? 
Yeah, surprise you.

1158
01:26:00,111 --> 01:26:01,852
This I got to see.

1159
01:26:03,375 --> 01:26:05,377
Oh, we don't have any bread.

1160
01:26:05,421 --> 01:26:06,813
Oh, who needs bread?

1161
01:26:06,857 --> 01:26:07,814
I do.

1162
01:26:07,858 --> 01:26:09,990
You don't really need bread.

1163
01:26:10,034 --> 01:26:11,514
Okay, forget it.

1164
01:26:11,557 --> 01:26:15,387
[SPEAKS FRENCH FLUENTLY]

1165
01:26:15,431 --> 01:26:18,564
Oh. Okay. I'll take this
upstairs and start lunch.

1166
01:26:18,608 --> 01:26:19,739
Do we need some wine?

1167
01:26:20,262 --> 01:26:21,219
No, I'll get some from my place.

1168
01:26:21,263 --> 01:26:24,570
And, Mo! Don't run
away this time.

1169
01:26:26,398 --> 01:26:27,878
Go learn how to cook.

1170
01:26:40,586 --> 01:26:41,979
[SPEAKS FRENCH]

1171
01:26:42,719 --> 01:26:44,373
Xavier?

1172
01:26:46,549 --> 01:26:48,377
Xavier, are you here?

1173
01:26:55,558 --> 01:26:56,733
Guess what I found?

1174
01:27:02,565 --> 01:27:04,001
[SPEAKING FRENCH]

1175
01:27:08,658 --> 01:27:10,573
[QUESTIONING IN FRENCH]

1176
01:27:13,271 --> 01:27:14,446
[SPEAKING FRENCH]

1177
01:27:15,317 --> 01:27:17,406
ISABELLE: Are you American?

1178
01:27:18,581 --> 01:27:20,235
MO: Yes.

1179
01:27:20,278 --> 01:27:22,237
Chantal lives right...

1180
01:27:22,976 --> 01:27:24,195
over there.

1181
01:27:31,158 --> 01:27:33,117
But she is on vacation now.

1182
01:27:35,032 --> 01:27:37,295
She'll be back in September.

1183
01:27:41,647 --> 01:27:44,128
Well, thank you.

1184
01:27:46,435 --> 01:27:48,263
Please,

1185
01:27:48,306 --> 01:27:51,266
use the lift. It works now.

1186
01:27:55,705 --> 01:27:57,707
Everything's back to normal.

1187
01:28:06,150 --> 01:28:08,326
No, thank you. I'd rather walk.

1188
01:28:13,375 --> 01:28:14,506
[DOOR CLOSING]

1189
